 cause), we simply test it!  We \\\'test\\\' by describing an episode and breaking it out into these elements, the A (Antecedents), B (Behavior), and C (Consequences). If there is a strong relationship between these elements, the ABCs, then it is very likely that we have isolated CAUSE.  Isolating a typical pattern of responding may involve many hours of very deliberate, direct observations. Behavior analysis stresses the importance of an objective record of the child\\\'s behavior as the basis for determining whether or not the desired change has occurred.\r\n', 'Basic Behavior Operations', '', '', '{\"1\":{\"110101\":\"1.01a\",\"110201\":\"1.02a\"},\"3\":{\"130101\":\"3.01a\",\"130102\":\"3.01b\",\"130103\":\"3.01c\",\"13022421905072\":\"3.02x2(seg2)\",\"13022421905073\":\"3.02x2(seg3)\",\"130301\":\"3.03a\",\"130302\":\"3.03b\",\"130303\":\"3.03c\",\"130305\":\"3.03e\",\"1303071905072\":\"3.03g(seg2)\"},\"4\":{\"140201\":\"4.02a\"},\"5\":{\"150101\":\"5.01a\",\"150102\":\"5.01b\",\"150103\":\"5.01c\",\"150201\":\"5.02a\",\"150202\":\"5.02b\",\"150301\":\"5.03a\",\"150401\":\"5.04a\",\"150402\":\"5.04b\",\"150403\":\"5.04c\",\"150404\":\"5.04d\",\"150409\":\"5.04i\",\"150601\":\"5.06a\",\"1506021\":\"5.06b1\",\"1507022\":\"5.07b2\",\"1508012\":\"5.08a2\",\"1509012\":\"5.09a2\"},\"6\":{\"160401\":\"6.04a\",\"160402\":\"6.04b\",\"160403\":\"6.04c\",\"1607021\":\"6.07b1\",\"1607022\":\"6.07b2\",\"1608\":\"6.08\"},\"8\":{\"1802032\":\"8.02c2\",\"1805011\":\"8.05a1\",\"1805023\":\"8.05b3\",\"1807022\":\"8.07b2\",\"1807032\":\"8.07c2\"},\"9b\":{\"190402\":\"9.04b\",\"190403\":\"9.04c\",\"190601\":\"9.06a\"},\"10\":{\"2101009\":\"10.10i\",\"2101201\":\"10.12a\"},\"11\":{\"21102022\":\"11.02b2\",\"21107012\":\"11.07a2\",\"21107017\":\"11.07a7\",\"21108015\":\"11.08a5\"},\"9A1-3\":{\"190001500\":\"9A.04i6\",\"190001490\":\"9A.04i5\",\"190000120\":\"9A.01b3\"},\"\":{\"80409214\":\"DI_214\",\"109000\":\"1pt.01a\",\"109070\":\"1pt.03\",\"128000\":\"3pt.01a\",\"128010\":\"3pt.